The paper proposes a retrieval scheme for biomedical question answering based on neural network word embeddings. This involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques, which are commonly associated with the arXiv categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and possibly neural networks (cs.NE).
